^#5aa9d6;Vanilla races now all have access to glitch hairstyles.^reset;

Applies to npcs as well. Art entirely from vanilla assets.

apex - black
avian - matches talons
floran - matches flowers
human - matches undies
hylotl - black
novakid - bronze

For more, click the MEGATHREAD link from the steam page.

